Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.data.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DrawableObject

    public class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements DrawableObject
    This is class holds all the Informations about a specific GameObject (e.g. a building) Especially which type it is, if its movable, what image should be drawn etc.
